call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: The ball is last touched by Gallinari (ATL) before it goes out of bounds.
Snell (ATL) legally contests Mills' (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Capela (ATL) slightly extends his arm into Murray (SAS) during the pick but the contact is marginal.
Young's (ATL) pass attempt is kicked by Poeltl (SAS).
Murray (SAS) delivers contact to Young's (ATL) body as he begins the upward shooting motion during his jump shot attempt.
Young (ATL) commits a take foul on Murray (SAS).
Following the hand off, DeRozan (SAS) turns into Hill's (ATL) body and the contact dislodges him.
Capela (ATL) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Gay (SAS).
White (SAS) makes contact with the ball and he dislodges it from Huerter (ATL).
Bogdanovic (ATL) makes contact to Murray's (SAS) body during his driving shot attempt.
Murray (SAS) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Hill (ATL) legally contests DeRozan's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Capela (ATL) establishes himself in a legal position in Murray's (SAS) path and he absorbs the oncoming contact during the pick.
Capela (ATL) makes contact to DeRozan's (SAS) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Murray (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position during Young's (ATL) driving shot attempt.
Gallinari's (ATL) arm appears to make contact with the ball during DeRozan's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Gallinari (ATL) is already in White's (SAS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Poeltl (SAS) and Capela (ATL) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Gay (SAS) makes contact with Gallinari's (ATL) arm as he is bringing both hands to the ball.
Gallinari (ATL) is already in Murray's (SAS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Gay (SAS) places a stayed hand to Young's (ATL) hip as he defends the driving shot attempt, and contact is marginal.
White (SAS) is already in Snell's (ATL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.

Hill (ATL) moves through White's (SAS) space and dislodges him from his legally obtained screening position.  After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined the foul occurred prior to the release of DeRozan's (SAS) shot attempt.
Murray (SAS) is already in Snell's (ATL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Snell (ATL) moves forward into DeRozan's (SAS) body and delivers contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Capela (ATL) is already in Mills' (SAS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.  The reaction from Mills is not consistent with the contact from Capela.
White (SAS) is moving alongside Young's (ATL) path and the marginal contact is caused by Young.
Capela (ATL) and White (SAS) briefly engage and disengage as they position themselves for a potential rebound.
White (SAS) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Gay (SAS) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
